name: Tabazuma
description: THIS SALE IS FOR ONE BEAD similar to the beads listed in the picture. Each bead is sold seperatly. The beads in the pictures are samples of the bead/beads you will get. They are priced PER bead and made to order. Order a as few or as many as you need. These are some of my most popular beads. These colorful square tabs range in size only slightly from approx. 10×10x10mm to 15×15x10mm Please allow up to two weeks for completion of your order All of my beads are one-of-a kind, made one-at-a time by me in my Des Moines, Iowa, studio—The Torch Porch. All of my beads are properly kiln annealed for a life everlasting, and have been cleaned, inspected and then cleaned some more! I use mainly Moretti and Lauscha (soft) glass. PLEASE email me if you have any questions. I answer ALL emails quickly! Thanks for stopping by!
